---

## What's NOT in Atlas (by design)

Hugging Face, browser automation, captcha, telegram, scheduler, web UI,
burner emails, account creation, profiles, Node/npm, Playwright, the
`.remember`/`.plugin-config` plugin cruft. None of it. Atlas is a small
Python proxy and nothing else.

